results.name: Coprime semiprimes: a(n-1) and a(n) are the closest coprime semiprimes.
comment: The slowest increasing sequence of semiprimes with coprime neighbor terms.
program: (PARI) lista(nn) = {my(vsp = select((x->(bigomega(x) == 2)), vector(nn, k, k)), i = 1, last); while (i <= #vsp, print1(vsp[i], ", "); last = vsp[i]; while(gcd(vsp[i], last) != 1, i++; if (i>#vsp, break)););} \\ _Michel Marcus_, Jun 25 2019
